folder: Gramercy Park South & Gramercy Park (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
Gramercy Park South, north side, between Gramercy Park East and Gramercy Park West, showing the main entrance gate to Gramercy Park, a private ground for residents of this exclusive residential area.

About 1915.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Manhattan: Gramercy Park South - Gramercy Park (East)

folder: Gramercy Park East & Gramercy Park (South), Manhattan, NY
text:
34, and 36 Gramercy Park East, at and adjoining the N.E. corner of Gramercy Park South, showing The Gramercy Park (9-stories) and the Gramercy Park Club Apartments (12-stories), as seen from Irving Place (extreme foreground), Gramercy Park South and across Gramercy Park. July 7, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Manhattan: Gramercy Park East - Gramercy Park (South)
